# ==========================================================
# .env — Environment Variables (NEVER commit this file!)
# ==========================================================
# Copy this file, rename to .env, and fill in your real keys.
# .env is already listed in .gitignore so it won't be pushed
# to GitHub accidentally.
# ==========================================================

# --- CHOOSE ONE API AND FILL IN YOUR KEY ---

# Option 1: Anthropic (Claude) — https://console.anthropic.com
